### Daily / weekly completion reports (2026-05-04)

- Added daily completion report from daily-plan checklist state.
- Source of truth:
  - child checklist rows in the daily-plan task;
  - `IS_COMPLETE=Y` means done;
  - checklist `members` identify responsible users;
  - parent checklist group name is used as fallback.
- Daily report behavior:
  - adds a comment to the daily-plan task;
  - sends a Telegram report to `TELEGRAM_REPORT_CHAT_ID` or the latest registered Telegram chat;
  - tags responsible users by Telegram username for each open checklist item;
  - does not move open items to the next day.
- Weekly report behavior:
  - scans daily-plan tasks in the selected week range;
  - aggregates all open checklist items;
  - sends a weekly Telegram report tagging all responsible users with open items at once;
  - if a weekly CRM task exists for `weekly_digest`, adds the weekly report as a comment there too.
- Telegram commands:
  - `@LLMeets_bot итоги вчера`
  - `@LLMeets_bot итоги 2026-05-04`
  - `@LLMeets_bot итоги недели 2026-05-04 2026-05-08`
- CLI commands:
  - `python -m meeting_digest_bot daily-report --yesterday`
  - `python -m meeting_digest_bot daily-report --report-date 2026-05-04 --force`
  - `python -m meeting_digest_bot weekly-report --current-week`
  - `python -m meeting_digest_bot weekly-report --week-from 2026-05-04 --week-to 2026-05-08 --force`
- Cron on VPS:
  - `CRON_TZ=Europe/Kyiv`
  - every day at `09:00`: `daily-report --yesterday`
  - every Friday at `16:00`: `weekly-report --current-week`
